                                                                             SNOWMAN GAME

Bring the snow back to the snowman planet by stacking the snowballs through the sky and space all the way home.

Directions:
1. Make sure you have pygame and random
2. Download the Snowman_game.py and all the images to the same folder
3. Play to your hearts content

How to play: 
Stack the snowballs by moving the bottom snowball left and right using the left and right arrow keys
Be sure to catch a snowball before time runs out...the bottom is melting
BEWARE of falling coal, it instantly melts 3 snowballs
LUCKY catch the snowman and instantly gain 3 snowballs
NICE catch the snowflake and enjoy speedy snowballs
